'''巨帶蛇'''（[[學名|學名]]：''Thamnophis gigas''）是[[束帶蛇屬|束帶蛇屬]]中最大的[[蛇|蛇]]。它們主要是水生的。

==生物及生態==
巨帶蛇是[[美國|美國]][[加利福尼亞州|加利福尼亞州]][[中央谷地|中央谷地]]濕地的[[特有種|特有種]]。它們於水溫20℃以上時最為活躍；若水溫較低，它們則會躲在地底。它們主要吃[[魚類|魚類]]及[[青蛙|青蛙]]。

==保育狀況==
由於濕地被大幅的破壞，巨帶蛇也受到威脅。<ref name="U.S. Fish 1999">U.S. Fish & Wildlife Service. 1999. Draft Recovery Plan for the Giant Garter Snake.  Portland, Oregon.</ref>它們在[[聖華金谷|聖華金谷]]只餘下很少的數量<ref>U.S. Fish & Wildlife Service. 1993. Endangered and Threatened Wildlife and Plants; Determination of Threatened Status for the Giant Garter Snake. Portland, Oregon.</ref>，並已從以往98%的分佈地消失。<ref>{{Cite web|author=California Reptiles & Amphibians|url=http://www.californiaherps.com/snakes/pages/t.gigas.html|title=''Thamnophis gigas'' - Giant Gartersnake|accessdate=2010-11-19|archive-date=2020-11-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109215924/http://www.californiaherps.com/snakes/pages/t.gigas.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>在[[莎加緬度山谷|莎加緬度山谷]]（Sacramento Valley）的情況稍為好些，因為當地種植[[稻米|稻米]]及[[運河|運河]]形成了它們的棲息地。<ref name="U.S. Fish 1999"/>若稻米收割後，它們則會遷到附近的地方。<ref>{{Cite book|author=Wylie, G.D., M.L. Casazza, and L.L. Martin|year=2004|title=Monitoring giant garter snakes in the Natomas Basin: 2003 results. Progress report for The Natomas Basin Conservancy|publisher=USGS, BRD Dixon Field Station|pages=75pp|url=http://www.werc.usgs.gov/dixon/pdfs/Official%20Report%20Natomas%202003.pdf|access-date=2010-11-19|archive-date=2016-12-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161221162124/https://www.werc.usgs.gov/dixon/pdfs/Official%20Report%20Natomas%202003.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>除了失去棲息地外，入侵的[[掠食者|掠食者]]如[[美國牛蛙|美國牛蛙]]也限制了它們的數量。<ref>{{Cite journal|author=Wylie, G.D., M.L. Casazza, and M. Carpenter|year=2003|title=Diet of bullfrogs in relation to predation on giant garter snakes at Colusa National Wildlife Refuge|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_california-fish-and-game_summer-2003_89_3/page/139|journal=California Fish and Game|volume=89|issue=3|pages=139-45}}</ref>現有措施恢復濕地的環境供它們棲息，但其效用則有待確定。

